      "code": "def tokenize(text):\n    return normalize_ar(text).split()\ndef token_f1(a, b):\n    A = tokenize(a)\n    B = tokenize(b)\n    setA = set(A)\n    setB = set(B)\n    inter = setA & setB\n    if not setA or not setB:\n        return 0.0\n    prec = len(inter)/len(setB)\n    rec = len(inter)/len(setA)\n    f1 = 2*prec*rec/(prec+rec) if (prec+rec)>0 else 0.0\n    return f1, prec, rec, inter, setA, setB\n\nf1, prec, rec, inter, setA, setB = token_f1(full_substring, ayah_text)\n(f1, prec, rec, inter)",
